   <div>
    <h1 style="padding: 25px 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; color: #000; padding-bottom: 10px;">枪展实况｜独家解读顶级枪械品牌的最新产品！</h1>
   </div> 
   <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #999; padding-bottom: 23px; text-align: center;">
    <a href="account_junwu233.shtml" class="accountlink">junwu233</a> &nbsp; 2017-01-20
   </div> 
   <div style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: #000;" id="content"> 
    <h2><span style="line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px;">作者：&nbsp;Sean&nbsp;</span></h2>
    <p><span style="line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px;">本文已获得WILDER授权<br /></span></p>
    <p><span style="line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px;"><br /></span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">美国时间1月18日，SHOT Show进入第二天。各路明星汇集，枪神Jerry展台亲送签名、奥运铜牌得主Corey Cogdell携奖牌宣传代言产品、UFC拳王李康也低调现身……</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5625" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvssxUudRjpYHhOrUPLOk1kVcbicowUyZjjX2SZTib3ibEruQTPsDunq5Lw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲枪神Jerry</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvuJFLVtu90F7oINqk5ffk7jcVJCQ8X6uNfMqfgly1nORyMibPNxibc4Rw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲奥运铜牌得主Corey Cogdell</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvBK81ia5EQKsT9jPxMHRDvKnEXKGsyDMtboF5gxGwJWJiczAmsYS2C4Wg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲UFC拳王李康和枪械专家Sean Song合影</span></strong></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">接下来让我们跟随WILDER枪械专家Sean Song的独家解读，深度了解2017 SHOT Show几大知名枪械品牌的最新产品！（文末有彩蛋）</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <section>
         <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">HK（Heckler &amp; Koch）</span></strong></p>
        </section>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这个在1949年建立的德国公司曾在初期生产制造日用品，但当时由于德国东西集团对峙，西德要重新建立武装力量，HK公司的创始人开始制造军品，最终成为了世界上最著名的军火制造商。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">HK手枪</span></strong></p>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvr6KpeKtZI13GHpCVNdlhhbib6iczgOnLKI29xSvZF42IrD29wuicIYRQw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲HK公司的P30SKS，口径为9mm</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这是目前所有手枪中最受欢迎的一把，也是最小巧的一把，更多的被用来作为随身携带和隐匿携带，非常方便。正因为这把枪过于小巧，握把比较短，使用起来不太舒服，个人不太喜欢。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvA8HK758uZBPEs8m7Keaibmyue8ia5sYED2ot5gYic7anSnUXuiaTxlUS4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲HK公司的P30L，同为9mm手枪</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这把枪的尺寸大小和握柄非常舒服，属于全尺寸配枪，非常精准。这把枪最近非常火，金&middot;里维斯的新片《John Wick》（《急速追杀》）中拿了两把P30枪出现。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.8375" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvo6vR8biccqhv0sqoleZpJdS7ibUNjnNND4tzsaUCbro3IWKYxdr6sC7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.5867507886435331" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvQ2icZePnrcyzLbeEpbLeKc7wKkSicUQa4HvnWXbm6HA4RrfGAdt5fRYA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng" data-type="png" data-w="634" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲《急速追杀》剧照，主角用的枪就是P30和P30L</span></strong></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvdyKj6xzXbQnWarumfLeOzGVF1dytdNNmaVDpDqtBtsjKshh4aNuEYA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲这也是P30系列中的一款――P30S</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">相对于前两款枪，这款枪长短居中，也是可以随身隐匿携带的手枪。握把比SKS长很多，使用起来比较舒服；枪管比P30L稍短一些，除此之外没有更多的差别。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvC3V44d3HicL6YGmaia9V38ZClAczEPyZAcItWWCTzI3N0sQsvnOO4vvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲VP40</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvHziaGfDquTnaYkibiaq2QKoZEs4JddpF4LSEE4GNPMjBT0ibRUsFu1X0fw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲VP9</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">上面这两款枪属于HK的VP家族，分别VP9和VP40，数字代表了口径（VP9是9mm，VP40就是.40口径）。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvibm26kyPvqfkLyInjub2Wwh14wjcQpvib9Vhs8IiaDYuAbBe2TNFsrcyQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲VP40配有消音器的版本</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvROFomA1J7nyKt9IOF9hWvFfPZABdibAILJszKFDCOSZqc6D7SOPV3wQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲VP9配有消音器的版本</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">VP系列和其它枪相比来说比较特殊，属于无击锤击发，而且没有保险――因此VP系列通常给专业的警务人员使用，子弹上膛之后不容易退弹，唯一的保险在扳机，这就增加了一定的危险性，不建议平民和新手使用，操作不顺会有一定的风险。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvaOwtpPtFfubJd3ArSyxRib0nT2Yqk6DqwovAdqUduvFpDXrFNrTxOpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲Mark23，.45ACP</span></strong></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Mark23是历史上唯一被称为“进攻手枪”的手枪，应海军陆战队要求专门设计，是可以在冲锋时候使用的手枪。这款枪采取了当时非常先进的O-Ring系统，保证枪管枪膛紧密程度，使精准度达到了最高。同时使用2段式结构导轨，很好地缓解了后坐力。本人有一把，我认为是.45口径中最准的一把。虽然这把枪非常有名，但不得不说算是一个过时的产品了。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">注：&nbsp;O-Ring系统说的是枪管上套个橡胶细环，这样枪管与滑膛之间可时刻保持弹性接触，减少枪口的偏心震动，能明显增加精准度。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvbkzmUic1W3ZXDleJnmIcUiapexuyibQrRqXKnd4ic2Byv7rYgD2NcQK1ibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲HK45，最新一代.45口径的手枪</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这款枪在美国评价非常非常高，HK融合了USP、P2000、Mark23等有利经验研制出HK45。使用2段式结构导轨控制后坐力，使用了和Mark23相同的O-Ring系统提高精度。HK45在设计中改进了Mark23枪身太长、握柄太粗的缺点，因此达到了使用体验的高峰。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">HK45可以说集HK之前所有手枪的优点于一身，是目前市面上最受欢迎的一款手枪。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvNDeXEd7V31we0oNb0OpRsuUwUvo1aIQcLuGK08AO5AUE05x9ciaHCcQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲HK45的COMPACT版本</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">HK45的COMPACT版本属于随身携带型，枪管和握柄在长度上有所缩减，更适合随身携带和隐匿持枪。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvQXP3MEGRLfPUNqZXbQeEgkmBPRdqttuv53OExxIv0b6htiaJubz1NoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲USP 45 tactical</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">最早的USP设计沿用至今天，凭借精准度在市场上仍非常受欢迎，虽然精准度非常好，但属于上世纪的产品，无法和HK45匹敌。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">HK步枪</span></strong></p>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvXg8BjaaTuPOiaUicsziazSMUpm8Bnjzxnhfz4wZOzAIIPNqBJb26Q5JRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲&nbsp;HK416，口径5.56</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">就是这一款步枪干掉了本拉登。现在美国海豹突击队装备的就是这款步枪，用的是Piston系统（活塞系统），增加步枪的稳定性，使它在任何艰苦的条件下都能正常使用（不同于传统版本的M4在潮湿或者沙土情况下会发生卡弹，这把枪绝对不会）。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvnJ3xcu4zXT8Dhj4zhpB10AALTHXzwn0icsibFGBy3wJ9ARNTpBSXnicPQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvGJzW8Q9Yho7Ss8ELiaKPo2LoWozDSLohlGTqlSxwhpzMevRLibib9GnMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲HK762（军版HK417），口</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">径7.62*51（俗称的.308口径）</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">通常活塞带动操作系统会影响精准度，但这把枪将这二者完美结合，这把枪的精准度在半自动步枪中名列前茅，甚至可以达到第一。根据个人喜好的不同，选择护手长短。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这两把枪非常精准耐用，共同的缺点是重量稍重，不适合长期携带。当然这对于受训的军人来说不影响，但对于平民来说这两把枪还是稍微重了一点。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvQgT0PUACrTPNIibBibapeS7QZibERl9ibA32eicl5PD2bp1uRuxLT4RgR0Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲G36C，口径5.56</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">G36C解决了上述两把枪比较重的问题，使用了全塑料枪身，因此经过长时间使用后会发生枪管过热的现象，对射击精度有一定影响，现在美国市场上已经不再流通。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">虽然不再生产，这款枪凭借它强悍又帅气的外形仍然受到枪友的喜爱追捧。这把枪也经常在电影中出现，最新的电影就是史泰龙《敢死队》，电影中大部分人用的都是G36。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.45625" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanv8ztJicDnP2xszMw00gP8CF4ufsTWnBgj6Z6GicaQmWzubHFMFmda4nzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲《敢死队》剧照</span></strong></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <section>
         <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">Sig Sauer</span></strong></p>
         <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        </section>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">在1853年西格（SIG）公司成立的时候，他们可能也想不到以做马车出身的他们之后会变成世界上最有话语权的军械生产商。如今，没人敢轻视西格绍尔的每一款新产品。他们的产品工艺先进、零件精度高、一致性好，零件之间完全可以互换，经过长久的发展，西格绍尔已经形成了系列枪族，其中最著名的当属西格绍尔P系列手枪。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">Sig Sauer手枪</span></strong></p>
        <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br /></span></strong></p>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvAkdgzibKdIicwbFU5ial4Xpa3DURpH3L0Dz9aBKDG25Ku05r4utviblAYQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲西格绍尔P226</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">非常经典的型号，经过多年发展仍然没有发现缺陷。这款枪是在HK的Mark23之后，在海军陆战队要求下生产的，采用全金属枪身，枪入手的感觉稍重，但不影响它的精准度。我认为这把枪非常适合新手，安全系统做的非常好，在卸下弹夹之后扳机不能被扣动（防止在退下弹夹后误发枪膛中的子弹），提高安全系数。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">据悉，现在中国的军队在尝试按照同样的规格自主研制MP22手枪，试图取代现在的92式手枪。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvbAWzVKOk6JqOcBahB9sNCHN7I8iaZiaZr7o79VQibFiaT7HO8NTz4ibearQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲P210 Target</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvVUkgsOibxwmZWV1rWr3JYuiczOrCt9ian7P8aJFvUM9j7jsicNRBmhm5BQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲P210 Super Target</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">P210是非常了不得的一款枪，被誉为“9MM枪王”，据说是9mm口径中最精准一把。P210 Super Target的枪管更长，因此比P210 Target精准度还高一些。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这两把枪在美国停产多年，但鉴于大家对这把枪的喜爱程度，现在重新生产。新产品采用了纯木制握把，非常舒服又有手感，枪底座和枪膛的密合程度非常高。如果Mark23是.45口径的枪王，那么P210称为9mm枪王毫不为过。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvZV62PHdkASv2GSEg6qBnWkxaL8Q2Bem7Rdic5kR3CEjgAOh32Iyic7vw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲P320</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">P320是目前在美国最热卖的一款手枪，也是西格绍尔为数不多的采用塑料作为枪身的手枪。这把枪被设计用来随身携带和隐匿持枪，把P226一切不必要的功能简化，做到最简单精巧，因此枪管和握柄非常短小，使用起来不太舒服。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvcz4b4Q3WzJQLf5b3dsgeK1O1oQvdDoMibZdnf2wAVXMVb1f9OA6xCjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲P938</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">一款非常受女性喜爱的手枪，我个人认为观赏性大于实用性，通常被设计的比较可爱、美观。图中这款被设计成受女性欢迎的玫瑰金颜色，上面还有激光雕纹。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">Sig Sauer步枪</span></strong></p>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvhq9O0HhU4JPIjySR0vds2vqecZwYv8G5QDlS6gloKekH4hxpicx7QZg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲西格绍尔最新AR系统步枪</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">为了让枪更加精准，最新AR系统的步枪采用了直接进气式而没有使用活塞式。虽然精度提高，但无法在恶劣条件下使用，而且在使用完毕之后必须及时清理，否则会卡壳堵塞，因此这款枪更适合比赛或竞技。&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvSMibkIicjic4wxg938uvW1JkQoumRsGVqjFFeNT9zGlPMyoyOCicM68tKg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲西格绍尔的旧款步枪</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">和HK步枪一样采用了活塞系统，但精准性远远达不到HK的水平。这款枪更适合作战或紧急情况下的防卫用途。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvJHK7Q0mFuicJDPjwTZKibIRRtgzcEedW896E2Mus3Tg16mY26MkLUqOA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲SBR，口径.556</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvKOCQXI8cuFN84WhibBuPTY5QTFaOJmXjlv6Cs1q9ghgPwT0WricEPrZg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲SBR，口径9mm</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">SBR――Short Barrel Rifle。SBR的枪管比较短，托把可以折叠，非常便于携带，因此收到了银行抢匪的青睐。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvxDMtIu7ffL3Xyvw8aia9ibbFQ2clcGWRgWDZALIwwKuYGYW3icAyctxjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲西格绍尔不仅枪做得非常好，还致力于子弹的设计和发展，不断提高子弹的杀伤力和精准度。图为西格绍尔设计的子弹的样板图。</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <section>
         <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">NightHawk</span></strong></p>
         <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        </section>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">NightHawk（美国夜鹰）是一家专门进行个人武器高级定制的公司，他们公司的口号也非常震撼人心：“我们一直能做到最好！”。在这个口号之下，夜鹰的定制服务质量非常高，即使在竞争激烈的美国M1911市场上，夜鹰公司生产的定制版M1911手枪也被公认是第一名。如果说HK是奔驰，西格绍尔是奥迪，那么夜鹰就是当之无愧的劳斯莱斯。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvM9dDN7oJyR1ichjZLrnravL5ibiaH6Ux3Spiaua9TCBo70Lb5EFaX0MCYA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvmR0niaB9z1zhBYQbb59u39u42VzcZ1Gl5rd9zblYiaW8wNO4SKy9txmQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvCCKPVAT5NQQ7HQSibYHnErDvSEf5wxcReO73AlVoMMrWX7B96GyN59Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">NightHawk的M1911所有零件都是由工匠一点点打磨，才能制造出完美的密合程度、保证枪精准性，在精准性和紧密程度上做到了顶峰。只有用过NightHawk才知道它和普通M1911的差别，公司承诺在30yard远的距离，子弹能够洞穿硬币那么大的孔。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanv9Q75jm75wtDlLricpjguP9anY8B7Gia8p6U40GQzyhibqCOQLZMIcQpyg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲德国Korth和NigthHawk共</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">同打造的战术型左轮手枪</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这把转轮是德国Korth和NigthHawk共同打造的战术型左轮手枪，无论从扳机、用料、枪管、后期完成处理都达到了最顶级的手枪水平。这把枪的特色在于虽然本身口径是麦格农357，但可以随时随地拆卸换成9mm子弹，一枪可以两用。但如果是用于家防，个人比较推荐.357麦格农，因为威力更大一些。</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br /></span></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <section>
         <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">FN</span></strong></p>
         <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
        </section>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;比利时的FN公司驰名全球，在1889年建厂，如今已经洋洋洒洒百年有余。FN在初建厂的时候和著名枪械设计师约翰&middot;M&middot;布朗宁合作，推出了不少FN-勃朗宁武器，也由此开启了FN的辉煌时代。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>FN手枪</strong></span></p>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanveAccoIrWibvHW4yMVJP1JR2jq0THo1GEzjqt75xdScKO2ibCf2kErib5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲FN很特殊的一把手枪57（Five seveN）</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">FN57虽然是手枪，但使用步枪子弹，射速很快，子弹杀伤力很大、穿透力也很强。因为子弹比较轻，所以弹容量非常大，可装20发子弹，在手枪中算是最多的了。如果20发全部装了步枪弹，那么可以击穿防弹玻璃和防弹衣，因此这把枪也被称为“警察杀手”。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这把枪的枪身很轻，全部使用合成塑料制成，正因为如此，很对人认为这把枪的手感不好。而且在保险和滑膛部分做的非常紧致，使用起来稍微有一些不舒服。即使FN57有这些缺点，但瑕不掩瑜，这款枪仍旧是一把非常棒的手枪。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvBSjEV7WpyAkqmibgbyCiaIdyogCqCO0tI53WatBNCmwziaBal3HyU2FDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲PS90和57的对比，这两把枪都</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">是cs中常见的武器，子弹可以通用</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvrdsSMDbq4iaaquG0eqibcxyZkzyboYNozZfhAMZRicw2Ds0ztt5tshib7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲FNX-45，.45口径</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">FNX-45，这把枪现在在美国市场上非常火，到达了重金难求的地步。这把枪使用.45手枪弹，装弹量为15发，实力不容小觑。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvicfY457JNppp9LdvawmlDqEwxWWxfe6hJcOOYAvYCyicKJ6ktiaDKibNTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <section>
     <section powered-by="xiumi.us">
      <section>
       <section>
        <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">FN步枪</span></strong></p>
       </section>
      </section>
     </section>
    </section>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvUdF07xp96mTb6Z8WuWPLwG0xCibicAicc3QOZJb3l17CnuGyLc6aopoXg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanv9fqKC0hZXb95AhTe3VojtnoJcGCrum6vxUkAWH93v5ZGY2491tSqkg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲FN M16(M4军用版)</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">上手试了一下，扳机偏硬，这也正符合了军枪的设计，感觉非常不错。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvYOib2nJSdqXV6QjJJCKf9Do5UUpEstxogIbRYFic5n8UBKFzniaMmwkCg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲配备了Trijicon的红点枪瞄</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanv9teHVs7fCIRppC5Ib18WU6nqUyZwTMxlUzPP73C42Cnv6Rz4dn2k6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvwLJk0nfJ0r2tSIVJ5FN0NUyhHWhC1lkxqaiawkFCXzj6LLS82RWibaYg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲FN M249S</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">著名的班用机枪，火力压制必须使用的武器。</span></p>
    <p><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanv5rxMN8uqVj8z5T8NW2hO5FiawD7DX3MwUkwTZY6srX8KibRiakBAOEQhg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvyIS6BxXETeOMc8B9twlfloIGzV2FnJQIIlEDhsP21OicP0fliad9ZoEg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvPicEx3cbBTNImcNbHm3R1crXRMfZ2h6u0a6l4ZVA0JeDPNGw9znVexg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvPz9uIHRfBZm4R95mmxrUTxVuWYPZ3Oe8y3Hiavqm9nrw7or2iah57VPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲Scar 16</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">FN最著名的Scar系列之一――Scar 16。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanv6XIQP0yZsMmvtKt3cfaMdsommsvATP6ARdSKgLCAnq3bvK3jvIPVCg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvN8fsAYnicxMB8wDCdP1bhPN4RurwaEmxCictvto3kd5vibibx5iadnxrjUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">今年FN带来了Scar系列的新产品――Scar20。目前这把枪只在军队投放，暂不对民间销售。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvzabWO1zxjDIhiaRT9Lt04TZFoccIafpT8gVUqnIIgL2V6coa2AwW3aA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvibtfiaMeZicXtWaAq1L2vtttzYEAKtp0tKX9lczlSXrITXWic6B8E4wHzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲FN最经典的狙击步枪：SPR和Ballista。</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">这两款枪可以说是精准射击的顶尖产品了，枪发展到这个地步已经几乎没有任何缺点可言。</span></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="1.3328125" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanv9AXydsqFQlNiaBNJErm04wiay8oOfsJLgIicql4xHV94GSxQMJ3RkJ8iag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲Ballista使用了三段式保险，分别是锁紧、</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">锁紧扳机但可以拉栓退出子弹、击发位置</span></strong></p>
    <p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="img.jsp?id=794688&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FqXq7QC3HhfJLtCvklPrJRqBicwSqPTanvCYZ7ajPRpcJzCx4PXCibmtGwZVvcX58gicdjVrDfbNofw3v6k8tBm9tw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" /></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;">▲枪口制退器特写</span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12px;"><br /></span></strong></p>
    <p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-align: right;">本文源于：WILDER</span></span></p>
